import PageHeading from "../components/page-heading.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/main.astro";
---

<Layout title="Cookie Policy - Bangla Web Fonts">
  <section class="relative z-20 max-w-3xl mx-auto my-12 px-7 lg:px-0">
    <PageHeading
      title="Cookie Policy"
      description="Last updated: 15 March 2025"
    />

<p class="mt-4">Welcome to <a href="https://banglawebfonts.pages.dev" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Bangla Web Fonts</a>. This Cookie Policy explains how we use cookies, caching, and similar technologies on our website.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help improve your experience by remembering preferences and analyzing traffic.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">We use cookies for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2">
            <li><strong>Performance and Security:</strong> Cloudflare uses cookies to enhance website security and optimize load times.</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Cloudflare Analytics may set cookies to collect anonymous data about website traffic and usage patterns.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">3. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">We use Cloudflare services, which may set cookies as part of their security and analytics features. You can read Cloudflare’s cookie policy <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/cookie-policy/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">4. Service Worker and Offline Storage</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Our website uses a service worker to enable offline functionality as part of a Progressive Web App (PWA). This service worker:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2">
            <li>Caches website content on your browser to improve performance and allow offline access.</li>
            <li>Does not collect or send any personal data to our servers.</li>
            <li>Only stores data locally on your device, which you can clear at any time through your browser settings.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">5. Managing Cookies and Storage</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">You can manage or disable cookies through your browser settings. You can also clear cached data stored by the service worker at any time by clearing your browser’s storage and cache.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">If you have any questions, please contact us at <a href="https://banglawebfonts.pages.dev/contact" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">our contact page</a>.</p>


  </section>
</Layout>